               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <br/>
To report SUSPECTED ADVERSE REACTIONS, contact Bausch + Lomb, a division of Valeant Pharmaceuticals North America LLC, at 1-800-321-4576 or FDA at 1-800-FDA-1088 or www.fda.gov/medwatch
 </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20190724"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="id_link_8e6cd111-05d0-570d-e053-2995a90ab41f">
               <id root="8e6cd111-05cf-570d-e053-2995a90ab41f"/>
               <code code="34068-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DOSAGE &amp; ADMINISTRATION SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Apply the ointment every 3 or 4 hours for 7 to 10 days, depending on the severity of the infection.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>FOR OPHTHALMIC USE ONLY</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20190724"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="id_link_8e6cd899-b7eb-a24c-e053-2a95a90a692e">
               <id root="8e6cd899-b7ea-a24c-e053-2a95a90a692e"/>
               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>HOW SUPPLIED</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Bacitracin Zinc and Polymyxin B Sulfate Ophthalmic Ointment, USP is available in tubes with an ophthalmic tip applicator in the following size:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>3.5 g tube </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>DO NOT USE IF CAP AND NECKRING ARE NOT INTACT.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Storage</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Store between 15°-25°C (59°-77°F). KEEP TIGHTLY CLOSED.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Keep out of reach of children</paragraph>
